{"type":null,"faqId":38975,"title":"为什么闹钟有时候会提前震动，有时候延迟震动呢？","answer":"<p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-indent:24.0pt;\nline-height:normal;\ntext-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other\"><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">原因是因为您启动了智能闹钟功能。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-indent:24.0pt;\nline-height:normal;\ntext-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other\"><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">如果您启用了智能闹钟功能，当手环检测到您处于浅睡状态时，会提前震动叫醒您。您可以根据手环界面提示，向上滑动屏幕或者点击屏幕最上方</span><span style=\"font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\"> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\">X </span></b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">关闭闹钟。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-align:center;text-indent:24.0pt;\nline-height:normal;\ntext-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';\nlayout-grid-mode:both;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150908090715583001.png\" style=\"width:129.75pt;height:123pt\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-indent:24.0pt;\nline-height:normal;\ntext-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other\"><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">闹钟震动时，点击屏幕其它位置或者不做任何操作，手环会给您</span><span style=\"font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">分钟的小睡时间，在</span><span style=\"font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">分钟后再次震动叫醒您。手环最多延迟震动</span><span style=\"font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">次。</span></p>\n<br>\n</p>","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"4285","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441673016000,"seriesProductName":"B0-Honor","visitedTimes":32,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}